{"tid":838950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MX 十月起堂食「日日無飲管」","createTime":"2018-09-27T13:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T02:37:36.000Z","uid":164435,"like":20,"dislike":300,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"22accc6228836112a78752ed76ab14d7977c2237","tid":838950,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/mx-21_6G85f_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmx-21_6G85f_1200x0.png&h=7c441ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>愈來愈多食肆加入「無飲管」的行列，為減塑出一分力。美心旗下連鎖快餐店 MX 在店內貼出告示，宣布由10月2日起實施「日日無飲管」，堂食凍飲將不提供飲管。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》記者今日在觀塘康寧道的MX分店內，發現店內貼出「日日無飲管」告示，宣布10月2日起堂食凍飲將不提供飲管。不過外賣及冰桶飲品則不受此限。<br />\n<br />\n泛民東區區議員徐子見今日亦在康怡分店內，見到「日日無飲管」公告。他在Facebook寫道：「美心都開始推無飲管日，雖只限堂食，但總算是好開始！」<br />\n<br />\nMX於2018年6月已曾推出「無飲管日」，每逢周三不主動向顧客提供飲管，鼓勵市民實踐綠色生活。今次MX是進一步將「無飲管日」擴展至一周七日。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》向美心方面查詢，「日日無飲管」是否會成為恆常措施，以及會否擴展至美心集團旗下其他食肆，暫待回覆。"},{"pid":"139414ebdd6f6813e46a6a7eb574b2ad78d02d96","tid":838950,"uid":5253,"like":203,"dislike":2,"score":201,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"本身已經係同類型最難食個間 仲要搞埋d咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係搵鬼食"},{"pid":"8d086e7abe91ca5678a2e53e39531194130bf0c4","tid":838950,"uid":132587,"like":202,"dislike":0,"score":202,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:54:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">mx堂食「日日無人」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23b8a8da9cc5771bcbc915f7636f3c03b06d488","tid":838950,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8d086e7abe91ca5678a2e53e39531194130bf0c4","tid":838950,"uid":132587,"like":202,"dislike":0,"score":202,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:54:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x